snippet.title: Celebs Who Aren't Fans Of Leonardo DiCaprio
snippet.description:
Leonardo DiCaprio was a talented child actor who grew into an award-winning A-lister. He seems to have it all and has consistently put out top-notch performances for his adoring fans.

But despite all the adoration, the star of the Basketball Diaries and Titanic still seems to have ruffled a few feathers in Hollywood.

For instance, George Clooney spoke with Esquire magazine in 2013 about a basketball game in which DiCaprio and he played. Clooney recalled DiCaprio delivering a subtle threat before the game but was handily beaten on the court. Clooney even threw shade at the final score.

To find out more about the final score of this story and other celebs who aren’t fans of Leonardo DiCaprio, watch this video.
